reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 25, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Received this product and it was very well packaged. Each part was wrapped with plastic to prevent scratching. The hardware was attached and clearly marked on the box so it was not lost. The directions were pretty simple and easy to follow, the only critic I have is you have to be careful in what way you attached each part together because it may be the wrong way. There isn’t a clear picture to decipher what direction. So a bit of problem solving. The end product was beautiful and very comfortable. I weigh 180 at 5,4 and I could comfortable cross my legs and relax. The table is very nice with a glass top finish. I would give it a 4.9/5 just because directions weren’t super clear, but overall great product

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice Affordable Set
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. After wanting rocking chairs for so long I spent a long time searching for a set that was affordable, nice looking, and easy to assemble.Since I didn’t want to wait for my husband’s help, I decided to assemble it myself. It took me a solid hour because I screwed some parts backwards 😂… anyways, assemble was pretty easy. Just make sure to account for all parts before starting and tight the bolts evenly. Like, don’t make one tight while the others are lose while assembling. It will be more difficult to align the other screws/holes and the panels won’t fit.The issues I had was that some of the screws were damaged and they didn’t go all the way trough. I went to Home Depot and bought replacements because I wasn’t going to disassemble anything at that point! 😅🏃🏽‍♀️💨 I called costumer service and they gave me a partial refund for the hassle! The bottom cushions have zippers, but the top ones don’t. The cushions do not have a string to tie them to the chair so they’ll blow away, and they’re not supper thick. I did find some strings of similar color and sewed it. Problem solved.Overall, I’m really pleased with the whole set! It’s sitting in a covered porch, so let’s see how it does when it rains. The manufacturer should add spare bolts and screws.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 20, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great for price!
reviews.reviewText: These came packaged well, no damage. Assembly was easy. The table is sturdy with a nice glass top. I love the look of these rockers on my deck. The seats are deep and comfortable. The pads are very thin and low quality but not a reason not to buy this set. I gave 4 stars because the plastic weaving is not very quality, but for the price it is exactly what I expected. I will probably have to rework it next year with a better quality strap, but that is something I enjoy doing. The frame is sturdy and that is what matters.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Value, Strong and Simple
reviews.reviewText: We just had our deck remodeled, and I needed some furniture, so I've been looking everywhere. I found this set and couldn't be happier. Sturdy, easy to assemble (took me about an hour), and they look great! The cushions are even just what I wanted, they're not thick and puffy but not super thin either. I love the black glass in the tabletop, it looks amazing. Great price, yet nothing is flimsy or cheaply made. All in all, very happy with this purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I Am Amazed
reviews.reviewText: I am so happy with this product. I searched for hours looking for the right set. This was packaged so well it was hard to open. Nothing was damaged. Glass is beautiful, cushions are so comfortable, the chairs are very sturdy. For the money I paid I think I did very well. It did take a little while to put together. But when complete it was well worth it. It was delivered much sooner than expected which was great because it was a gift. Highly recommend this seller.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Affordable and Comfortable chairs
reviews.reviewText: The chairs were fairly easy to assemble. The color of the cushion (turquoise) is bright and has not faded all summer. Very nice pop of color on the patio. We have not left the cushions on when it rains- we bring them inside so I can't attest to how they are after a storm. Comfort able to sit on and a little wider seat than most we've purchased. Overall, a nice chair at an affordable price!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to Put Together & GORGEOUS!!!
reviews.reviewText: This is so wonderful, sturdy, beautiful and they are rockers!!! I will definitely get another for each of my sons. Well worth it for a great price!!! Thank you!!! Happy camper for sure!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Worse than IKEA
reviews.reviewText: Lovely pieces. Comfortable. Cushions are bare bones, so upgrade asap. Assembly instructions may as well not exist. Horrible. 5 different screw sizes that all fit anywhere. Took me HOURS to find where I went wrong with it all to assemble the side table. Love, but NEVER again.
